{"tid":1322872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"某程度上，我要多謝安心偷食呢單野先令我呀媽醒覺","createTime":"2019-07-16T05:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:25:49.000Z","uid":1735,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0036ff37948d3663f501372f1bc2aac3d3df65","tid":1322872,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:28:58.000Z","msg":"佢本身係淺藍，久唔久都會話啲人搞搞震，所以一直都無乜兩句<br />\n<br />\n直至到之前偷食事件，佢見我睇條片睇到嘩嘩聲，就問我咩嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />安心偷食喎，你無睇過咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無！東方都無呢條片！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我幫你down個蘋果你自己睇飽佢<br />\n<br />\n估唔到嘅係，down咗蘋果佢唔單止淨係睇娛樂，仲睇好多時事，連東方都睇少咗，仲主動話唔睇tvb，我都好驚訝<br />\n<br />\n點都好，多謝許志安同黃心穎令我老母醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed61cb6c0f116e17e2d89ec4526f4627a3993490","tid":1322872,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:33:48.000Z","msg":"安仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e24dc8a7cbfc084b93bc4ce4f897f5be03abde0","tid":1322872,"uid":1735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"我會日日聽你啲歌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e275d0e821a83d3bef49dcc25b0a484a557e751f","tid":1322872,"uid":264965,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"安仔：我計在長遠"},{"pid":"c0228805b6df9958b44ec65fc08c5a3822ad8139","tid":1322872,"uid":43114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e275d0e821a83d3bef49dcc25b0a484a557e751f","tid":1322872,"uid":264965,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"安仔：我